{"image_id": "DOV_2012_page_26", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "10", "bbox": [608.6, 1554.7, 629.4, 1577.8]}, {"text": "contracts, primarily in the aerospace and defense markets of our Communication Technologies segment. Our total backlog", "bbox": [93.8, 108.3, 1149.6, 131.4]}, {"text": "relating to our continuing operations as of December 31, 2012 and 2011 was $1.5 billion and $1.4 billion, respectively.", "bbox": [93.8, 133.4, 1089.8, 156.4]}, {"text": "Competition", "bbox": [93.8, 183.4, 210.1, 206.4]}, {"text": "Our competitive environment is complex because of the wide diversity of our products manufactured and the markets served.", "bbox": [93.8, 233.4, 1149.6, 256.5]}, {"text": "In general, most of our businesses are market leaders that compete with only a few companies, and the key competitive factors", "bbox": [93.8, 258.4, 1149.7, 281.5]}, {"text": "are customer service, product quality, price, and innovation.  However, as we become increasingly global, we are exposed to", "bbox": [93.8, 283.4, 1149.7, 306.5]}, {"text": "more competition. Certain businesses in the Communication Technologies and Printing & Identification segments compete", "bbox": [93.8, 308.4, 1149.7, 331.5]}, {"text": "globally against a variety of companies, primarily operating in Europe and East Asia.  A summary of our key competitors by", "bbox": [93.8, 333.4, 1149.7, 356.5]}, {"text": "end market within each our segments follows:", "bbox": [93.8, 358.4, 478.1, 381.5]}, {"text": "Segment", "bbox": [198.3, 399.6, 274.7, 422.7]}, {"text": "End Market", "bbox": [486.1, 399.6, 595.6, 422.7]}, {"text": "Key Competitors", "bbox": [845.0, 399.6, 997.3, 422.7]}, {"text": "Communication Technologies", "bbox": [103.2, 425.0, 355.0, 448.0]}, {"text": "Consumer electronics", "bbox": [407.5, 425.0, 588.7, 448.0]}, {"text": "AAC Technologies, GoerTek Inc.", "bbox": [711.8, 425.0, 991.6, 448.0]}, {"text": "Medical technology", "bbox": [407.5, 454.1, 573.6, 477.2]}, {"text": "Sonion A/